OL,7,FWatch from ITVX: Spotting the symptoms
OL,8,Fof sepsis can be difficult but there
OL,9,Fare key signs to be aware of
OL,11,FSepsis is a life threatening reaction
OL,12,Fto an infection which sees the body
OL,13,Fattack its own organs and tissues, and
OL,14,Fwhile its impact can be deadly,
OL,15,Fspotting sepsis isn't so easy.
OL,17,FIt's estimated around 245,000 cases
OL,18,Foccur in the UK each year, according
OL,19,Fto the UK Sepsis Trust.
