OL,8,Flikely to get an infection that could
OL,9,Flead to sepsis, including babies,
OL,10,Fpeople aged over 75 and anyone who is
OL,11,Fdiabetic, has a weakened immune
OL,12,Fsystem, people with Down's syndrome
OL,13,Fand women after pregnancy.
