OL,7,FWhat is the treatment?
OL,9,FPeople who have sepsis might need to
OL,10,Fstay in hospital for several weeks.
OL,12,FThe quicker people arrive at hospital
OL,13,Fthe better because the condition can
OL,14,Fcause more damage very rapidly.
OL,16,FIt's like doctors will provide
OL,17,Fantibiotics within an hour to prevent
OL,18,Fthe risk of septic shock causing
OL,19,Forgans to fail.
